NAME
    Email::Enkoder - obfuscate email or html with randomized javascript

VERSION
    version 1.120830

FUNCTIONS
  enkode_mail
    Generates an obfuscated email link.

  enkode
    Generates obfuscated html out of arbitrary html.

HELPERS
  enkoders
    Returns the default enkoders used to obfuscate html.

  js_wrap_quote
    Takes a javascript string definition and wraps it to fit in a defined
    number of columns.

  js_dbl_quote
    Takes a piece of javascript and quotes and escapes it for use as a
    string definition.

SUPPORT
  Bugs / Feature Requests
    Please report any bugs or feature requests through the issue tracker at
    <http://rt.cpan.org/Public/Dist/Display.html?Name=Email-Enkoder>. You
    will be notified automatically of any progress on your issue.

